---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import FunctionPlotter from '../../../components/diagrams/FunctionPlotter.svelte';
---

<Layout title="Integration Methods" lang="en" backHref="/explore-math/en/grade-12/" backLabel="← Grade 12">
	<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Integration Methods</h1>
	<p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8">Substitution, integration by parts and more</p>
	<section class="prose max-w-none">
		<h2>Difficult Integrals</h2>
		<p>Not every integral is straightforward. Substitution and integration by parts help.</p>
		<h3>🧪 Experiment</h3>
		<p>f(x) = x·eˣ:</p>
	</section>
	<FunctionPlotter client:visible fnExpr="x * Math.exp(x) * 0.1" fnLabel="x·eˣ (scaled)" xMin={-5} xMax={3} yMin={-1} yMax={3} />
	<section class="prose max-w-none mt-8">
		<h3>💡 Methods</h3>
		<ul><li>Substitution: ∫f(g(x))·g'(x)dx</li><li>Integration by parts: ∫u·dv = u·v − ∫v·du</li><li>Partial fractions</li></ul>
	</section>
</Layout>
